        "cooked": "<p>\u4e2d\u6587\u7248\u5728\u4e0b\u65b9\u3002</p>\n<p>Hi everyone, we\u2019re thrilled to announce the release of <strong>Parametric Model Maker v1.1.0</strong>! This is a significant update focused on improving the user experience for everyone. We\u2019ve completely redesigned the platform\u2019s interface from the ground up to be more intuitive, powerful, and beautiful.</p>\n<h1><a name=\"p-553792-a-fresh-new-look-the-redesigned-interface-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-553792-a-fresh-new-look-the-redesigned-interface-1\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>A Fresh New Look: The Redesigned Interface</h1>\n<p>The first thing you\u2019ll notice is the brand-new look and feel. We\u2019ve moved away from the old layout to introduce a more modern and user-friendly experience.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>New Home Page:</strong> Say goodbye to the \u201cCommunity\u201d pop-up! We now have a dedicated home page that beautifully showcases trending, most downloaded, and latest models. This provides much better visibility for your creations and makes discovery easier for all users.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Redesigned Editor:</strong> The model customization page has been completely refactored. It\u2019s not just about looking better; it\u2019s about being more functional. Users can now easily view the model\u2019s description, see stats, and engage with comments, all within a cleaner, more organized layout.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1><a name=\"p-553792-for-our-creators-key-changes-to-your-workflow-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-553792-for-our-creators-key-changes-to-your-workflow-2\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>For Our Creators: Key Changes to Your Workflow</h1>\n<p>While the platform looks different, all the powerful features you rely on are still here\u2014we\u2019ve just adjusted their access points to create a cleaner interface. Here are two important changes to note:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Code Editor Location</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>To provide a simpler experience for users who only need to adjust parameters, the code editor for OpenSCAD models is now collapsed by default.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>How to Access:</strong> When viewing a model that allows code editing, you will now see a <strong>Code</strong> button on the left-hand panel. Clicking this will open the familiar code editor, allowing you to make and save your changes.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/2/e/2e5bde68ed109c6963509c6832488485b96ff4f9.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/6C6N4Xo5v5XkJcRu7Ypttjsb4tr.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/2/e/2e5bde68ed109c6963509c6832488485b96ff4f9_2_517x273.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"6C6N4Xo5v5XkJcRu7Ypttjsb4tr\" width=\"517\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/2/e/2e5bde68ed109c6963509c6832488485b96ff4f9_2_517x273.jpeg, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/2/e/2e5bde68ed109c6963509c6832488485b96ff4f9_2_775x409.jpeg 1.5x, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/2/e/2e5bde68ed109c6963509c6832488485b96ff4f9_2_1034x546.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"343D35\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1920\u00d71013 92.2 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>Testing Your Models Before Upload</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Testing your local <code>.scad</code> files is now more streamlined. We\u2019ve integrated this functionality into the new Creator Panel.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>How to Access:</strong> Click on the <strong>Creator Portal</strong> button on the top navigation bar. From the dropdown menu, select <strong>Open SCAD File</strong>. This will take you to the editor where you can load and test your model directly in our environment before you decide to upload it.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/8/f/8fcd9f54f68e68ad12b448ca7cc4bfb4d096bdf3.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/kw8OYAtIwjhavCcsqL6KVmWr9qX.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/8/f/8fcd9f54f68e68ad12b448ca7cc4bfb4d096bdf3_2_690x255.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"kw8OYAtIwjhavCcsqL6KVmWr9qX\" width=\"690\" height=\"255\" srcset=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/8/f/8fcd9f54f68e68ad12b448ca7cc4bfb4d096bdf3_2_690x255.jpeg, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/8/f/8fcd9f54f68e68ad12b448ca7cc4bfb4d096bdf3_2_1035x382.jpeg 1.5x, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/8/f/8fcd9f54f68e68ad12b448ca7cc4bfb4d096bdf3_2_1380x510.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"181718\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1920\u00d7712 77.7 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a name=\"p-553792-openscad-and-libraries-updated-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-553792-openscad-and-libraries-updated-3\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a><strong>OpenSCAD and Libraries Updated</strong></h2>\n<p>To ensure you have access to the latest features and bug fixes, we have updated our backend engine.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>OpenSCAD Version:</strong> We are now running a version based on commit <code>c8fbef05ba900e46892e9a44ea05f7d88e576e13</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>BOSL2 Library:</strong> The popular BOSL2 library has been updated to version <code>99fcfc6867e739aa1cd8ffc49fe39276036681f1</code>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This update is all about building a better foundation for the future of Parametric Model Maker. We believe these changes will make it easier for users to discover and customize your amazing work, and for you to create and test your models more efficiently. We can\u2019t wait to see what you create with these new tools!</p>\n<p>Happy modeling!</p>\n<hr>\n<details>\n<summary>Chinese Version \u4e2d\u6587\u7248\u672c</summary>\n<p>\u5404\u4f4d\u521b\u4f5c\u8005\u4eec\u597d\uff0c<strong>\u53c2\u6570\u5316\u6a21\u578b\u7f16\u8f91\u5668 V1.1.0</strong> \u6b63\u5f0f\u53d1\u5e03\uff01\u8fd9\u662f\u4e00\u6b21\u91cd\u5927\u66f4\u65b0\uff0c\u65e8\u5728\u4e3a\u6240\u6709\u7528\u6237\u63d0\u5347\u4f53\u9a8c\uff0c\u5e76\u4e3a\u6211\u4eec\u5b9d\u8d35\u7684\u521b\u4f5c\u8005\u4eec\u4f18\u5316\u5de5\u4f5c\u6d41\u7a0b\u3002\u6211\u4eec\u5bf9\u5e73\u53f0\u754c\u9762\u8fdb\u884c\u4e86\u5f7b\u5e95\u7684\u91cd\u65b0\u8bbe\u8ba1\uff0c\u4f7f\u5176\u66f4\u52a0\u76f4\u89c2\u3001\u5f3a\u5927\u548c\u7f8e\u89c2\u3002</p>\n<h1><a name=\"p-553792-h-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-553792-h-4\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>\u7115\u7136\u4e00\u65b0\uff1a\u5168\u65b0\u8bbe\u8ba1\u7684\u754c\u9762</h1>\n<p>\u9996\u5148\u662f\u5168\u65b0\u7684\u5916\u89c2\u548c\u611f\u89c9\u3002\u6211\u4eec\u6452\u5f03\u4e86\u65e7\u7684\u5e03\u5c40\uff0c\u5f15\u5165\u4e86\u66f4\u73b0\u4ee3\u5316\u3001\u66f4\u53cb\u597d\u7684\u7528\u6237\u4f53\u9a8c\u3002</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>\u5168\u65b0\u7684\u9996\u9875\uff1a</strong> \u544a\u522b\u4e4b\u524d\u7684\u201c\u793e\u533a\u201d\u5f39\u7a97\u5427\uff01\u6211\u4eec\u73b0\u5728\u6709\u4e86\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e13\u5c5e\u7684\u9996\u9875\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u66f4\u597d\u5730\u5c55\u793a\u6d41\u884c\u3001\u6700\u591a\u4e0b\u8f7d\u548c\u6700\u65b0\u7684\u6a21\u578b\u3002\u8fd9\u4e3a\u60a8\u7684\u521b\u4f5c\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u66f4\u597d\u7684\u66dd\u5149\u5ea6\uff0c\u4e5f\u8ba9\u6240\u6709\u7528\u6237\u66f4\u5bb9\u6613\u53d1\u73b0\u65b0\u6a21\u578b\u3002</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>\u91cd\u65b0\u8bbe\u8ba1\u7684\u7f16\u8f91\u5668\uff1a</strong> \u6a21\u578b\u7f16\u8f91\u9875\u9762\u5df2\u5b8c\u5168\u91cd\u6784\u3002\u8fd9\u4e0d\u4ec5\u4ec5\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u66f4\u597d\u770b\uff0c\u66f4\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u529f\u80fd\u66f4\u5f3a\u5927\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u7528\u6237\u53ef\u4ee5\u5728\u4e00\u4e2a\u66f4\u6574\u6d01\u3001\u66f4\u6709\u6761\u7406\u7684\u5e03\u5c40\u4e2d\uff0c\u8f7b\u677e\u67e5\u770b\u6a21\u578b\u63cf\u8ff0\u3001\u7edf\u8ba1\u6570\u636e\u548c\u8bc4\u8bba\u3002</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1><a name=\"p-553792-h-5\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-553792-h-5\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>\u81f4\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u521b\u4f5c\u8005\uff1a\u5de5\u4f5c\u6d41\u7a0b\u4e2d\u7684\u5173\u952e\u53d8\u5316</h1>\n<p>\u867d\u7136\u5e73\u53f0\u770b\u8d77\u6765\u4e0d\u4e00\u6837\u4e86\uff0c\u4f46\u60a8\u6240\u4f9d\u8d56\u7684\u6240\u6709\u529f\u80fd\u90fd\u8fd8\u5728\u2014\u2014\u6211\u4eec\u53ea\u662f\u8c03\u6574\u4e86\u5b83\u4eec\u7684\u5165\u53e3\uff0c\u4ee5\u521b\u5efa\u4e00\u4e2a\u66f4\u7b80\u6d01\u7684\u754c\u9762\u3002\u4ee5\u4e0b\u662f\u4e24\u4e2a\u9700\u8981\u6ce8\u610f\u7684\u91cd\u8981\u53d8\u5316\uff1a</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>\u4ee3\u7801\u7f16\u8f91\u5668\u4f4d\u7f6e</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>\u4e3a\u4e86\u7ed9\u90a3\u4e9b\u53ea\u9700\u8981\u8c03\u6574\u53c2\u6570\u7684\u7528\u6237\u63d0\u4f9b\u66f4\u7b80\u6d01\u7684\u4f53\u9a8c\uff0cOpenSCAD\u6a21\u578b\u7684\u4ee3\u7801\u7f16\u8f91\u5668\u73b0\u5728\u9ed8\u8ba4\u662f\u6298\u53e0\u7684\u3002</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u5982\u4f55\u8bbf\u95ee\uff1a</strong> \u5f53\u60a8\u67e5\u770b\u4e00\u4e2a\u5141\u8bb8\u4ee3\u7801\u7f16\u8f91\u7684\u6a21\u578b\u65f6\uff0c\u60a8\u4f1a\u5728\u5de6\u4fa7\u9762\u677f\u4e0a\u770b\u5230\u4e00\u4e2a <strong>\u4ee3\u7801</strong> \u6309\u94ae\u3002\u70b9\u51fb\u5b83\u5c06\u6253\u5f00\u60a8\u719f\u6089\u7684\u4ee3\u7801\u7f16\u8f91\u5668\uff0c\u8ba9\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u8fdb\u884c\u5e76\u4fdd\u5b58\u66f4\u6539\u3002<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/4/c/4cac4aa946ddb4380e60003cd3324af7a8d22b79.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/aWhq5WKRysmHl8dWt042werxU6Z.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/4/c/4cac4aa946ddb4380e60003cd3324af7a8d22b79_2_690x365.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"aWhq5WKRysmHl8dWt042werxU6Z\" width=\"690\" height=\"365\" srcset=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/4/c/4cac4aa946ddb4380e60003cd3324af7a8d22b79_2_690x365.jpeg, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/4/c/4cac4aa946ddb4380e60003cd3324af7a8d22b79_2_1035x547.jpeg 1.5x, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/4/c/4cac4aa946ddb4380e60003cd3324af7a8d22b79_2_1380x730.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"343D35\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1920\u00d71017 88.5 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>\u4e0a\u4f20\u524d\u6d4b\u8bd5\u60a8\u7684\u6a21\u578b</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u60a8\u672c\u5730\u7684 <code>.scad</code> \u6587\u4ef6\u53d8\u5f97\u66f4\u52a0\u6d41\u7a0b\u5316\u3002\u6211\u4eec\u5df2\u5c06\u6b64\u529f\u80fd\u6574\u5408\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u521b\u4f5c\u9762\u677f\u4e2d\u3002</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u5982\u4f55\u8bbf\u95ee\uff1a</strong> \u70b9\u51fb\u9876\u90e8\u5bfc\u822a\u680f\u7684 <strong>\u521b\u4f5c\u8005\u4e13\u533a</strong> \u6309\u94ae\u3002\u5728\u4e0b\u62c9\u83dc\u5355\u4e2d\uff0c\u9009\u62e9 <strong>\u6253\u5f00 SCAD \u6587\u4ef6</strong>\u3002\u8fd9\u5c06\u5e26\u60a8\u8fdb\u5165\u7f16\u8f91\u5668\uff0c\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u5728\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u73af\u5883\u4e2d\u76f4\u63a5\u52a0\u8f7d\u548c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u60a8\u7684\u6a21\u578b\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u518d\u51b3\u5b9a\u662f\u5426\u4e0a\u4f20\u3002<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/a/5/a5413d6b4c48442773fb97f878593b2db49ce0f4.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/nzUyCTkM894OZ9V3fHztFLkdSL2.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/a/5/a5413d6b4c48442773fb97f878593b2db49ce0f4_2_690x174.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"nzUyCTkM894OZ9V3fHztFLkdSL2\" width=\"690\" height=\"174\" srcset=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/a/5/a5413d6b4c48442773fb97f878593b2db49ce0f4_2_690x174.jpeg, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/a/5/a5413d6b4c48442773fb97f878593b2db49ce0f4_2_1035x261.jpeg 1.5x, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/a/5/a5413d6b4c48442773fb97f878593b2db49ce0f4_2_1380x348.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"181819\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1920\u00d7486 63.3 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a name=\"p-553792-openscad-6\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-553792-openscad-6\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a><strong>OpenSCAD \u53ca\u5e93\u66f4\u65b0</strong></h2>\n<p>\u4e3a\u786e\u4fdd\u60a8\u80fd\u4f7f\u7528\u6700\u65b0\u7684\u529f\u80fd\u548c\u9519\u8bef\u4fee\u590d\uff0c\u6211\u4eec\u66f4\u65b0\u4e86\u540e\u7aef \u5f15\u64ce\u3002</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>OpenSCAD \u7248\u672c\uff1a</strong> \u6211\u4eec\u73b0\u5728\u8fd0\u884c\u7684\u7248\u672c\u57fa\u4e8e commit <code>c8fbef05ba900e46892e9a44ea05f7d88e576e13</code>\u3002</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>BOSL2 \u5e93\uff1a</strong> \u5e7f\u53d7\u6b22\u8fce\u7684 BOSL2 \u5e93\u5df2\u66f4\u65b0\u81f3\u7248\u672c <code>99fcfc6867e739aa1cd8ffc49fe39276036681f1</code>\u3002</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u672c\u6b21\u66f4\u65b0\u65e8\u5728\u4e3a\u53c2\u6570\u5316\u6a21\u578b\u7f16\u8f91\u5668\u7684\u672a\u6765\u6253\u4e0b\u66f4\u575a\u5b9e\u7684\u57fa\u7840\u3002\u6211\u4eec\u76f8\u4fe1\u8fd9\u4e9b\u53d8\u5316\u5c06\u4f7f\u7528\u6237\u66f4\u5bb9\u6613\u53d1\u73b0\u548c\u5b9a\u5236\u60a8\u51fa\u8272\u7684\u4f5c\u54c1\uff0c\u5e76\u8ba9\u60a8\u66f4\u9ad8\u6548\u5730\u521b\u5efa\u548c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u6a21\u578b\u3002</p>\n<p>\u6211\u4eec\u8feb\u4e0d\u53ca\u5f85\u5730\u60f3\u770b\u5230\u60a8\u7528\u8fd9\u4e9b\u65b0\u5de5\u5177\u521b\u9020\u51fa\u4ec0\u4e48\uff01</p>\n</details>",
