        "cooked": "<p>I like the design and that you updated the BOSL lib, but why I can\u2019t increase the width of the editor window anymore?<br>\nNow it\u2019s really hard to develop with the parametric model maker and I have to develop with this tool, otherwise I wouldn\u2019t see when my project is to big and I run into the timeout while generating.<br>\nI hope you can change it back again.</p>",
