        "can_wiki": false,
        "cooked": "<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/pineapplebun_bbl\">@PineappleBun_BBL</a> is there a single location to easily find information about all the changes?</p>\n<p>Is this a single location containing all the documentation?</p>\n<p>A year or so ago I asked for a list that we could see of all the fonts and their typefaces available along with previews, I haven\u2019t seen this yet.  This amounts to a web page or a PDF resource that is greatly required.</p>\n<p>I love this solution, it is great work and powerful, the colour integration is commendable, but the documentation is lacking.</p>\n<p>It hurts new and seasoned developers alike.</p>",
